        <prompt>These images most clearly demonstrate the Progressive Era emphasis on:</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">Environmental determinism</option>
            <option letter="b">Political machines</option>
            <option letter="c">Nativism</option>
            <option letter="d">Prohibition</option>
        </options>
        <answer>a</answer>
        <explanation>The before-and-after photos reflect Progressive beliefs in environmental determinism - that improving living conditions would lead to social improvement and immigrant assimilation.</explanation>
